SLO       <title>Poglavje 5</title>
ENG       <title>Chapter 5</title>

SLO         <hi type="super">1</hi> ╓Opazujte╖, kako se drevesa pokrivajo z zelenimi listi in obrodijo sad. Zato bodite pozorni ┌in spoznajte┐ glede na vsa ┌Njegova dela┐ in spoznajte kako jih je On, ki živi na veke, tako naredil.
ENG         <hi type="super">1</hi> ╓Observe ye╖ how the trees cover themselves with green leaves and bear fruit: wherefore give ye heed ┌and know┐ with regard to all ┌His works┐, and recognize how He that liveth for ever hath made them so.

SLO         <hi type="super">2</hi> In ┌vsa┐ Njegova dela se ┌tako na veke┐ nadaljujejo iz leta v leto in vse naloge, ki jih izpolnjujejo Zanj, in ┌njihove naloge┐ se ne spreminjajo, ampak glede na to kakor je Bog odredil, tako so storjene.
ENG         <hi type="super">2</hi> And ┌all┐ His works go on ┌thus┐ from year to year ┌for ever┐, and all the tasks which they accomplish for Him, and ┌their tasks┐ change not, but according as God hath ordained so is it done.

SLO         <hi type="super">3</hi> In glejte, kako morje in reke na podoben način izpolnjujejo in ┌ne spreminjajo┐ svojih nalog ┌iz Njegovih zapovedi┐.«
ENG         <hi type="super">3</hi> And behold how the sea and the rivers in like manner accomplish and ┌change not┐ their tasks ┌from His commandments┐.

