SLO             <row><cell><hi type="super">4</hi> Toda vi – vi niste bili trdni niti niste izpolnjevali Gospodarjevih zapovedi,</cell></row>
ENG             <row><cell><hi type="super">4</hi> But ye—ye have not been steadfast, nor done the commandments of the Lord,</cell></row>

SLO             <row><cell> temveč ste se obrnili vstran in govorili ponosne in trde besede<opomba>(Glej i. 9, opomba in prim. Ps xii. 4; Dan vii. 8, 11, 20. Obtožba bogokletja je pogosta v xci-civ, npr. xci. 7, 11.)</opomba><r r="Ps.12.4">Ps 12,4</r><r r="Dan.7.8">Dan 7,8</r><r r="Dan.7.11">Dan 7,11</r><r r="Dan.7.20">Dan 7,20</r></cell></row>
ENG             <row><cell> But ye have turned away and spoken proud and hard words<opomba>(See i. 9, note, and Cf. Ps. xii. 4; Dan. vii. 8, 11, 20. The charge of blasphemy is frequent in xci-civ, e.g. xci. 7, 11.)</opomba><r r="Ps.12.4">Ps 12:4</r><r r="Dan.7.8">Dan 7:8</r><r r="Dan.7.11">Dan 7:11</r><r r="Dan.7.20">Dan 7:20</r></cell></row>

