ENG         <hi type="super">6</hi> (Then I asked Raphael the angel who was with me, and I said unto him: ‘This spirit—whose is it, whose voice goeth forth and maketh suit?’)E (And I asked Raphael the angel who was with me, and I said unto him: ‘This spirit which maketh suit, whose is it, whose voice goeth forth and maketh suit to heaven?’)Gg<opomba>(6. 7. Abel’s soul cries for "vengeance". Gen. iv. 10.)</opomba><r r="Gen.4.10">Gen 4:10</r>

