SLO       <p><hi type="bold">LXIX. Imena in funkcije (padlih angelov in) Satanov. Skrivna prisega.</hi></p>
ENG       <p><hi type="bold">LXIX. The Names and Functions of the (fallen Angels and) Satans: the secret Oath.</hi></p>

SLO       <title>Poglavje 69</title>
ENG       <title>Chapter 69</title>

