SLO         <hi type="super">8</hi> Četrtemu je bilo ime Pênemûe;<opomba>(Prim. פנימי 'notranji'.)</opomba> učil je človeške otroke grenko in sladko in jih naučil vseh skrivnosti njihove modrosti.
ENG         <hi type="super">8</hi> And the fourth was named Pênemûe:<opomba>(Cf. פנימי 'the inside'.)</opomba> he taught the children of men the bitter and the sweet, and he taught them all the secrets of their wisdom.

