ENG         <hi type="super">7</hi> And I recounted to him the whole vision which I had seen, and he said unto me: ‘A terrible thing hast thou seen, my son, and of grave moment is thy dream-vision as to the secrets of all the sin of the earth: it must sink into the abyss and be destroyed with a great destruction.

SLO         <hi type="super">8</hi> In zdaj, moj sin, vstani in prosi Gospodarja slave, ker si vernik, da bi na zemlji lahko ostal ostanek in da On ne bi uničil celotne zemlje.
ENG         <hi type="super">8</hi> And now, my son, arise and make petition to the Lord of glory, since thou art a believer, that a remnant may remain on the earth, and that He may not destroy the whole earth.

SLO         <hi type="super">9</hi> Moj sin, iz neba bo vse to prišlo na zemljo in na zemlji bo veliko uničenje.<opomba>(tj. od Boga določeno.)</opomba>
