ENG         <hi type="super">1</hi> <opomba>(1-9. The Deluge, and Noah's deliverance.)</opomba> And one of those four went to that white bull and instructed him in a secret, without his being terrified: he was born a bull and became a man, and built for himself a great vessel and dwelt thereon; and three bulls<opomba>(his three sons.)</opomba> dwelt with him in that vessel and they were covered in.<opomba>(Cf. x. 1-3 where Uriel visits Noah for the same end. To build the ark, Noah becomes a man.)</opomba><r r="Gen.7.16">Gen 7:16</r>

