ENG         <hi type="super">6</hi> But that vessel floated on the water, while all the oxen and elephants and camels and asses sank to the bottom with all the animals,<opomba>(i.e. the real animals.)</opomba> so that I could no longer see them, and they were not able to escape, (but) perished and sank into the depths.

