ENG         <hi type="super">7</hi> And again I saw in the vision till those water torrents were removed from that high roof, and the chasms of the earth were levelled up and other abysses were opened.<opomba>(The writer conceives the flood as caused by a cleaving of the depths of the earth, and stayed by their closing up. Cf. Jub. vi. 26; Prayer of Manasses 3.)</opomba>

SLO         <hi type="super">8</hi> Nato je vanje začela teči voda, dokler zemlja ni postala vidna. Toda to plovilo se je usedlo na zemljo in tema se je umaknila in pojavila se je svetloba.
