ENG         <hi type="super">13</hi> And when those twelve sheep had grown, they gave up one of them<opomba>(i.e. Joseph.)</opomba> to the asses, and those asses<opomba>(Midianites (v. 11).)</opomba> again gave up that sheep to the wolves,<opomba>(the Egyptians.)</opomba> and that sheep grew up among the wolves.

