ENG         <hi type="super">18</hi> And the sheep went to the wolves according to the word of the Lord, and another sheep<opomba>(Aaron.)</opomba> met it and went with it, and the two went and entered together into the assembly of those wolves, and spake with them and admonished them not to touch the sheep from henceforth.

