SLO         <hi type="super">3</hi> Ko je Matuzalem slišal besede svojega očeta Henoha – kajti pokazal mu je vse, kar je skrito<opomba>(ɑ: 'vsaka skrivna stvar' β.)</opomba> – se je vrnil in mu (jih) pokazal in ime tistega sina imenoval Noe, kajti on bo po vsem uničenju potolažil zemljo.<opomba>(Pomen imena Noe, podanega v 1 Mz v. 29, se tu ponovi.)</opomba><r r="Gen.5.29">1 Mz 5,29</r>
ENG         <hi type="super">3</hi> And when Methuselah had heard the words of his father Enoch—for he had shown to him everything in secret<opomba>(ɑ: 'every secret thing' β.)</opomba>—he returned and showed (them) to him and called the name of that son Noah; for he will comfort the earth after all the destruction.<opomba>(The meaning of the name Noah given in Gen. v. 29 is here repeated.)</opomba><r r="Gen.5.29">Gen 5:29</r>

